reviews.reviewText: I bought these chargers for my classroom so that I had extra chargers for myself and any of my students that might need to charge their phone during the day. Obviously, I have students that have a variety of different Apple cell phones and none of them have had issues in using this charger with their phone. This is a good affordable charger to have as a spare in case your other chargers breaker or go out.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 12, 2023
reviews.reviewText: The charger was great until the iPhone charging cables stopped charging a few weeks ago. One went, and I figured it’s fine because there’s another one, until that one stopped working as well. My friend bought the same charger and hers also stopped working but it was still in the return window so she was able to get a new one. I haven’t had it for that long-since August. I don’t understand why these cables never last.
